A man, along with his family, were followed to their home and robbed at gunpoint by four men on Sunday morning. According to the driver&#8217;s wife, four armed robbers followed her husband, who had just picked up his family from OR International Airport on Sunday. The robbers were driving a silver Hyundai accent 2016 model, said the woman, in a video posted on YouTube by Claire Gopaul. Watch the video below: